title: Lynyrd Skynyrd with Original Members
description:
VH1 Behind the Music
Lynyrd Skynyrd Uncivil War
All live clips from "Freebird the Movie"
Gone with the Wind

Live:
1976 Knebworth Fair (bad audio sync. Entire show minus Freebird is contained in FB the Movie Live Clips)
1975 Winterland in SF (with Ed King in B&W)
1975 Old Grey Whistle Test (with "only" two guitarists)
1976 Winterland in SF (with "only" two guitarists in B&W)
1977 Convention Hall in NJ (with Steve Gaines in B&W)
Plus part a few more live clips and a partial interview with former "Honkette" JoJo Billingsly
